# auto-bench cache: Linux binary builds + downloaded release archives.
/.cache/

# ── All local artifacts live under local/ — NEVER shared. ──
# Input datasets (downloaded / converted) AND raw results + run reports: every-
# thing regenerable via the drivers. We ship how to RUN the bench (drivers,
# converters, docs, and the datasets/ config manifest), never the data or the
# numbers. Drivers write reports to local/runs/; converters default to local/.
/local/
